t="308">\r\n<p>ビタの花\r\n216×164</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="galleryItem"><img src="../wp-content/themes/twentythirteen/images/fig04/images/quilt05.png" width="240" height="172">\r\n<p>島はにぎやか\r\n153×217</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="galleryItem"><img src="../wp-content/themes/twentythirteen/images/fig04/images/quilt06.png" width="240" height="343">\r\n<p>椰子の木\r\n213×149</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- / #btmArticle -->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- / #inlineCont -->\r\n\r\n</div></div></div>', 'Gallery Page', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '160-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-03 04:32:32', '2015-06-03 04:32:32', '', 160, 'http://caohagan.localhost/?p=306', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
